- Added build step for swift, node and yarn
- Fixes npm tests to refer to `npm/test` while looking for generated `node_modules`
- Fixes npm parser which was erroring out with a nil pointer dereferencing error while parsing nested dependencies. (Although a better fix is to use types and not maps)

pr_body: Tests [fail](https://github.com/opensbom-generator/parsers/actions/runs/5269868350/jobs/9528585714?pr=63) when running for poetry. This PR adds support for failing tests by setting up Python and poetry

- Refactor of the existing command `spdx-sbom-generator`
 - Contains doc handlers for both `v2.2` and `v2.3` 
 - Generated spdx and json SBOMs are mentioned below respectively

   -  https://gist.github.com/ba11b0y/cbad34ac266c323ac6c047817bfb880b
